<strong class='text-white'>Worsening with Rest:</strong> Pain and stiffness are worse at night or after periods of inactivity. <br/>
<strong class='text-white'>Improvement with Activity:</strong> Unlike degenerative pain, it improves with physical exercise. <br/><br/>
